    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 guidance for MRL 2 Class II devices. CFD predictions of hemolysis index agree with experimental measurements within 14.3% across all operating points. Relative hemolysis index RH < 1 for all 5 flow-speed combinations evaluated. The computational model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the CPB device COU.",
